recommendationRotationRadio

public void recommendationRotationRadio(boolean bEnable)
                                 throws GnException
Enabling this option will cause results to be sequenced in a radio-like fashion, otherwise results will be without sequencing.

Parameters:
bEnable - [in] True or false to enable or disable

Remarks:

This option is only applicable to Recommendations generated by GnRhythmQuery To enable Radio sequencing, define this option key with a True value. Without this option Rhythm might return you 5 Britney Spears tracks. With this option enabled Rhtyhm would never do that, it would mix it up more, like a radio station.
Throws:
GnException

stationDMCA

public void stationDMCA(boolean bEnable)
                 throws GnException
When creating a radio station, you have the option to enable DMCA rules, which reduce the repetition of songs and albums in conformance with DMCA guidelines. By default, DMCA is not enabled.

Parameters:
bEnable - [in] True or false to enable or disable

Remarks:

This option cannot be changed after the radio station has been created

GnException
